Class GAMuBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • GAMuBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GAMuListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class GAMuBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements GAMuListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of GAMuListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
